DESCRIPTION:Spray City Walls Graffiti Battle \nEvery 3rd Friday | 8 – 11 PM | Free Entry!\n\nGet ready to immerse yourself in a world of creativity\, colors\, and culture as we celebrate the beauty of art at Spray City Walls Graffiti Battle!\n\nHighlights of the event:• Live mural painting select artists• Delicious craft beers and beverages• Live music and entertainment• Artist market & vendors• Community engagement and more!\n\nDon’t miss the chance to be a part of this vibrant celebration of art and expression. Whether you’re an art enthusiast\, a foodie\, or just looking for a fun day out\, this event has something for everyone.Save the date and spread the word! We can’t wait to share this unforgettable experience with you.
URL:https://badastronautbeer.com/event/spray-city-walls-graffiti-battle/2026-07-17/
LOCATION:Bad Astronaut Brewery\, 1519 Fulton Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77009\, United States
CATEGORIES:Live Event,Market
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://badastronautbeer.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/spray-city-walls-houston-graffiti-art-market-battle.jpg
END:VEVENT
