SUMMARY:Punk Rock Garage Sale
DESCRIPTION:Insomnia Gallery and Deep End Records are excited to announce the date for our July Punk Rock Garage Sale!\n\nIf you haven’t caught on yet\, these happen on the 3rd Sunday of EVERY MONTH at Bad Astronaut brewing!\n\nWhile summer is heating up\, stay relatively cool as this event is ***ALL INDOORS!*** and the event space itself now has AC!\n\nThere will be OVER 50 VENDORS inside this massive adult playground of a venue which features pool tables\, foosball\, air hockey\, cornhole and more (and all FREE to play!)\n\nWe’ve got makers\, artists\, collectibles\, thrift and vintage\, music\, books\, video games\, movies and vendors selling so much more!\nIf you’re looking for a gift or to treat yourself\, come to Insomnia Gallery’s Punk Rock Garage Sale for a true chance to score!\n\nNEW VENDORS EVERY MONTH! We’ll mix in a few pro vendors and artists as well to bring you a truly unique market each and every month!\n\nAbout this event:Based on the punk rock garage sales that took place regularly at Walter’s Downtown\, Insomnia Gallery has been keeping this tradition alive for the last 6 years! DIY Forever!\nSale hours: 2:00pm – 6:00pm\nLocation: Bad Astronaut Brewing at 1519 Fulton\nFREE street parking on Sunday in addition to their back parking lot and grass parking lot!\n\n** INTERESTED IN SETTING UP? Contact deependhtx@gmail.com with a general description of the items you’d like to sell and we’ll get back with you asap! Table fee ranges from $15-$25 depending on setup size!
URL:https://badastronautbeer.com/event/punk-rock-garage-sale-3/2026-07-19/
LOCATION:Bad Astronaut Brewery\, 1519 Fulton Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77009\, United States
CATEGORIES:Live Event,Market
