SUMMARY:AIR HOCKEY TOURNAMENT
DESCRIPTION:Bad Astronaut & Photon Air Hockey Present \nAIR HOCKEY DOUBLES TOURNAMENT\nEvery Thursday | 7:30 – 10 PM | Free Entry\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJoin us every Thursday in the taproom for our exciting Air Hockey Tournaments! Whether you’re a beginner or an expert\, there’s a matchup for you. Enjoy thrilling double-elimination rounds with timed 3-minute matches and fantastic prizes for the winners. Test your skills and immerse yourself in the electrifying experience of Photon Blitz! Don’t miss out on the action!
